Dongfeng will bring to Russia crossover Fengguang 370 and pickup Rich New - website Driving www.zr.ru
Dongfeng Fengguang 370 is a representative of the popular class of cars in China, combining the advantages of a minivan and a crossover.
Another announced Russian premiere is the Rich New pickup truck.
Many Western firms of the Moscow International Motor Show this year decided to ignore, so the emptiness of the exhibition halls "Crocus Expo" will be filled by Chinese firms.
In particular, a powerful front will be Dongfeng Motor Corporation, which has great views on the Russian market and intends in the near future to offer our motorists a number of interesting innovations.
One of them will be the Dongfeng Fengguang 370 crossover, which went on sale in China this spring at a price of 55,900 yuan (just under 550 thousand rubles at the current rate).
For Russians, such a price list is unlikely to shine, and the issue of deliveries to our country is still under discussion.
In China, by the way, Fengguang 370 by the results of June sales managed to reach the 11th place in the list of the best-selling minivans, although due to the large road clearance (175 mm) and protective plastic shell on the lower perimeter of its body can be quite counted as crossovers.
Crossvan is built on the front-wheel drive platform of the Fengguang 360, the 370 has the same wheelbase of 2725 mm, but the body is slightly longer (4565 mm versus 4510 mm), the design is more solid, and the equipment is richer.
The salon is decorated with wooden planks, but shown in the photo a large vertical touch screen "like Tesla" on the central console was only on the early exhibition copies of the crossover, and the machines with "music" easier to sell.
Five of the seven seats are easy to fold, forming a flat loading area with a length of 1650 mm, the maximum volume of the trunk - 1500 liters.
