About the dynamic qualities of the machine, the manufacturer is modestly silent, but promises a sparing budget of the appetite owner at the level of 6.7 l/100 km.
The Rich New pickup is a well-known Russian Nissan NP300 Navara of the requested generation, but with a slightly refined Chinese stylistic design.
