At a similar price, Rich New will probably be of interest to Russians, because modern Japanese pickups have become excessively expensive.
Rich New is equipped with two engines of choice: gasoline 2.4 liters (137 hp) or turbo diesel 2.5 liters (116 hp).
The gearbox - only mechanics, drive - on the rear wheels, but there are modifications and with a hard-wired "front".
It will be on the stand Dongfeng and the new flagship sedan A9, its Russian premiere the representative office of the Chinese firm announced in June.
Minveno-like crossovers in the Chinese market are becoming more and more, some of the latest innovations - Cowin V3 and SWM X7.
Currently, the Russian Dongfeng line consists of two models: the S30 sedan and the H30 Cross hatchback.
In the seven months of this year, the dealers of the Chinese company sold 696 cars in our country.
Notifications on transport tax will stop sending by mail - website Driving www.zr.ru
The Tax Inspectorate has changed the procedure for sending notifications about property taxes.
All Russian car owners are accustomed to the scheme that has not changed over the years: in summer and autumn they receive a receipt for payment of transport tax for the previous year.
However, many will not be able to attend this year.
The fact is that the tax inspectorate changed the procedure of notification of citizens without excessive noise.
Those who are registered in the "Personal account of the taxpayer" on the official website of the agency nalog.ru, notifications will come in electronic form.
In the inspection, such Russians were automatically considered online users and cut them out of the standard, "paper" mailing.
The novelty will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
Everyone else will still receive the usual letters.
However, the possibility to return to the old scheme has and the owners of the account on the site.
To do this, they will have to visit the tax department during August and write a statement.
On the one hand, the new order is more modern and convenient.
The notification will appear in the "personal office" immediately after the compilation, while the letter will go a few days and may be lost at all.
In addition, the number of users of the Internet service of tax inspection exceeded 18 million people, which will allow the department to seriously save on postal mail.
On the other hand, the modest news on the inspection website is clearly not enough to inform citizens about the changed order.
Some could register in the "personal office" to receive a one-time service and have long forgotten about it.
These people will not wait for notifications by mail and, without knowing it, will fall into the category of non-payers with all the resulting consequences.
Access to the "Personal Account of the Taxpayer" is carried out in three ways: through the account of the portal gosuslugi.ru, by means of an electronic signature or by entering the login and password indicated in the registration card.
The latter can be obtained personally in any branch of the tax inspection (regardless of the place of registration).
We remind you that this year the transport tax must be paid by December 1.
The dispatch of notifications began in July.
